'''Tom Kenny''' is an American actor, voice actor, singer, and stand-up comedian who provided the voice of [[Biggs Darklighter/Legends|Biggs Darklighter]] in ''[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron II: Rogue Leader]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike]]'' and [[Nute Gunray]], [[Nahdar Vebb]], [[Tanivos Exantor Divo|Tan Divo]], [[Greedo]], and the [[Rodian]] [[Silood]] in ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' television series. He also voiced Nute Gunray in ''[[LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga]]''. He has also done numerous other voice roles, most notably the title character of [[Wikipedia:SpongeBob SquarePants|''SpongeBob SquarePants'']].

